HEADWORD: Onloft
<hw>On*loft"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Aloft; above
ground.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She kept her father's life <qex>onloft</qex>.</q>
